To install => npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled
PS S:\Project\BloggingApp_MERN\client> npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled


<!-- rafce  -->

For Routing install 
PS S:\Project\BloggingApp_MERN\client> npm i react-router-dom

For Global Context Use Redux Tookit 

npm install @reduxjs/toolkit

If you need React bindings:

npm install react-redux


  
